{"tid":23961,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"凍齋啡係有糖定冇糖","createTime":"2016-12-05T09:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T11:38:29.000Z","uid":5196,"like":2,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b31af7b0c9fd02d8c97db49930f2b44f336fc722","tid":23961,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"岩岩飲左杯甜既凍齋啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想叫人換, 仲比人話下次想走甜要叫齋啡走甜<br />\n但「齋」啡有糖仲叫算咩「齋」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁齋啡係有糖定冇糖?<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08bf546563e9bac3c6fd784135401976876a627","tid":23961,"uid":8207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"齋啡係指得咖啡<br />\n冇奶冇糖喎<br />\n<br />\n係咪d 大陸閪唔識呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303e1e5b9a23e4980898292627d30b9be7d62095","tid":23961,"uid":45728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"我做水吧 凍係有甜 熱就無<br />\n之前整凍齋啡無加糖水比人屌"},{"pid":"e1706e1ac141cc76dce1266452fc319e53bd8560","tid":23961,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"熱唔清楚 但係涷係一定有糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67966d4ede79b9c88f601ccc45f3d400a130c3f2","tid":23961,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"有糖冇奶真係好難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e757c3a107c27e29b3c17e0b58f27dbd3e138ea","tid":23961,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"茶記黎講<br />\n齋啡應該係純粹無奶<br />\n齋啡走甜/全走 先係無埋糖"},{"pid":"c7489ed1f33c0c4cd433d1f2aa43adc3c485335a","tid":23961,"uid":38690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:28:18.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"bb0d37c4b281b8ceec5ac4ec67ff289a041e689d","tid":23961,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶記黎講<br />\n齋啡應該係純粹無奶<br />\n齋啡走甜/全走 先係無埋糖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要咁做, d人係咪唔識個齋字點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adeb2f8bcf576c787461cefb6a5cd086f530323","tid":23961,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>茶記黎講<br />\n齋啡應該係純粹無奶<br />\n齋啡走甜/全走 先係無埋糖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要咁做, d人係咪唔識個齋字點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識解釋你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我做過水吧，我都係回想返個流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啡會一早倒定一壺出黎，加糖，放涼<br />\n呢個就係凍啡，出果時再加冰加奶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b6b9378ecc778428ebc00f71c96bde5595fef5","tid":23961,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"日本飲涷齋啡，係有微糖"},{"pid":"3ac8145da4a6c23cb5b664124a2eb7ca98968110","tid":23961,"uid":45132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5329676d007cf62f6cc1156f48ac00d25e9dfab8","tid":23961,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶"},{"pid":"58c8250b9128b9c571b7cd3ddb4660a29c87f5e3","tid":23961,"uid":27763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"飲左幾年 茶記一定會有糖， 你同啊姐講凍齋啡走糖 佢仲會笑你 齋左咪冇糖囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b2b9bc7d2899ba7635d6abb393c68e3c892163","tid":23961,"uid":19385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"齊啡有糖仲難飲過有奶有糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nblack才是男人的浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a72ca1541ef4c65af8fbfb4a555db88c77f0d0d","tid":23961,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶</blockquote><br />\n茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶<br />\n唔需要太執著個齋字<br />\n茶餐廳文化就係咁<br />\n菠蘿包又唔通有菠蘿咩"},{"pid":"706380fa3ac6317801df6b4b42055e07f48fd613","tid":23961,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>齊啡有糖仲難飲過有奶有糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nblack才是男人的浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先飲第一啖差d想噴返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c957ec123f51428583f4070e0090d4703bc834","tid":23961,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶</blockquote><br />\n茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶<br />\n唔需要太執著個齋字<br />\n茶餐廳文化就係咁<br />\n菠蘿包又唔通有菠蘿咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有人會飲有糖走奶既咖啡?<br />\n即係凍檸茶有糖走檸?<br />\n<br />\n難飲到飛起根本唔會有人飲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a91fe4eca353e4045b145bd38c3363eb578041","tid":23961,"uid":50771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"其實凍檸啡都好正"},{"pid":"8f89433eaf02ce88881db46a03a7ec4aad32534f","tid":23961,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶</blockquote><br />\n茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶<br />\n唔需要太執著個齋字<br />\n茶餐廳文化就係咁<br />\n菠蘿包又唔通有菠蘿咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有人會飲有糖走奶既咖啡?<br />\n即係凍檸茶有糖走檸?<br />\n<br />\n難飲到飛起根本唔會有人飲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己一個覺得唔好飲唔代表其他人都覺得唔好飲，<br />\n呢個世界好大，而地球亦都唔係圍住你黎轉呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ad5d29bcc7251825deeedafe6743e44714f2a1","tid":23961,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"茶記d凍飲根本垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524431d78f1112b153b27601c31d0dbe99eb64db","tid":23961,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶</blockquote><br />\n茶餐廳齋啡只代表走奶<br />\n唔需要太執著個齋字<br />\n茶餐廳文化就係咁<br />\n菠蘿包又唔通有菠蘿咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有人會飲有糖走奶既咖啡?<br />\n即係凍檸茶有糖走檸?<br />\n<br />\n難飲到飛起根本唔會有人飲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己一個覺得唔好飲唔代表其他人都覺得唔好飲，<br />\n呢個世界好大，而地球亦都唔係圍住你黎轉呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗疾住哂wo巴打<br />\n我相信世界咁大, 實有人覺得屎係好食既"},{"pid":"e1ca2d385be8f71ea5c8c4fa661475cf405a9d31","tid":23961,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>齊啡有糖仲難飲過有奶有糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nblack才是男人的浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先飲第一啖差d想噴返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都中過幾次伏<br />\n去開果間叫凍齋就已經冇奶冇糖<br />\n之前去第二間叫凍齋 一飲就想嘔 <br />\n同呀姐講重要比佢係到依依俄俄話走甜又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcffeec161c67cc40d09cd9fc0520af400e776b2","tid":23961,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗疾住哂wo巴打<br />\n我相信世界咁大, 實有人覺得屎係好食既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇新假期就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c839549e436913d54671fe90c7532bef5270c94","tid":23961,"uid":16066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"次次都叫凍齋啡走甜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfdac0cd1685fe3e0aeca581d6d6d4f0de3086a","tid":23961,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"仲有有好多茶記外賣熱飲會幫你落埋糖<br />\n所以要自己落糖的話叫之前要事先講明喲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}